42:03.626 --> 42:05.505
What are they fussing about?

42:05.588 --> 42:07.926
[Isabella] Looks like your mom's
really laying into Nora.

42:08.009 --> 42:10.557
Yeah, well, that's Eliza for you.

42:10.640 --> 42:12.351
